pageContext.claim: “Our relationship with Finland is a very close one and we’re always ready to help Finland. One of the things that is happening is you’re purchasing large amounts of our great F-18 aircraft from Boeing and it’s one of the great planes, the great fighter jets.”
pageContext.analysis: The Finish president, who looked surprised when Trump made this comment, later said there had been no such agreement to buy Boeing F-18 jets.
